Description:

History is a VDR plugin for maintaining a replay history.

Installation:

cd /put/your/path/here/VDR/PLUGINS/src
tar -xzf /put/your/path/here/vdr-history-X.Y.Z.tgz
ln -s history-X.Y.Z history
cd /put/your/path/here/VDR
make
make plugins
./vdr -P history
